%BB%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%9F"><span class="nav-number">1.1.5.</span> <span class="nav-text">如何杀死一个进程？</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F"><span class="nav-number">1.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">输入输出系统</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%AF%B7%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%8Csocket%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E7%A7%8D%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%8CBIO%EF%BC%8CNIO%EF%BC%8CAIO"><span class="nav-number">1.2.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">请介绍一下，socket编程的三种通信模型，BIO，NIO，AIO</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E5%99%A8%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86"><span class="nav-number">1.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">存储器管理</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E9%87%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AD%98%E7%A2%8E%E7%89%87%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9F"><span class="nav-number">1.3.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">怎么理解操作系统里的内存碎片，有什么解决办法？</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AF%E9%A1%B5%E5%BC%8F%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%EF%BC%9F"><span class="nav-number">1.3.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">什么是页式存储？</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E8%B0%83%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8E%E6%AD%BB%E9%94%81"><span class="nav-number">1.4.</span> <span class="nav-text">处理调度与死锁</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%9F"><span class="nav-number">1.4.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">系统如何提高并发性？</span></a></li><li clas